de.uni.freiburg.iig.telematik.sepia.parser.pnml

类 AbstractPNMLParser<P extends AbstractPlace<F,S>,T extends AbstractTransition<F,S>,F extends AbstractFlowRelation<P,T,S>,M extends AbstractMarking<S>,S,N extends AbstractPetriNet<P,T,F,M,S>,G extends AbstractPNGraphics<P,T,F,M,S>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.uni.freiburg.iig.telematik.sepia.parser.pnml.AbstractPNMLParser<P,T,F,M,S,N,G>
  • 类型参数:
    P - Type of Petri net places
    T - Type of Petri net transitions
    F - Type of Petri net relations
    M - Type of Petri net markings
    S - Type of Petri net place states
    N - Type of the Petri net
    G - Type of the Petri net graphics
    直接已知子类:
    AbstractPNMLCPNParser, AbstractPNMLPTNetParser

    public abstract class AbstractPNMLParser<P extends AbstractPlace<F,S>,T extends AbstractTransition<F,S>,F extends AbstractFlowRelation<P,T,S>,M extends AbstractMarking<S>,S,N extends AbstractPetriNet<P,T,F,M,S>,G extends AbstractPNGraphics<P,T,F,M,S>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract super class of the PNML parsers containing methods to read elements and attributes occurring in all net types.

    1.0
